  "description": "Discovery 6 as performance instrument: macroSeed=0.7. The seed latch fires on note-on, injecting a new LCG-derived 16-bit state from the engine's internal RNG. Every note played triggers a completely different organism from the same Rule 22 law. A single key contains multitudes — a C4 is never the same colony twice. Hold macroSeed at 0.7 for infinite variety. Lower it to 0.0 to commit to the current organism. This is generative improvisation: you are not playing notes, you are summoning organisms.",
